description: My place is close to Clemente's Maryland Crab House, United Artists Sheepshead Bay Stadium 14 IMAX Movie Theater, Fuel, Mitoushi, and Waldbaums. You’ll love my place because of the kitchen, the coziness, the high ceilings, and the location. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, and families (with kids).
